snippet.title: Mecha Force - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Learn about the story of Mecha Force and see action-packed gameplay in this new trailer for the upcoming VR game that blends mecha action with a roguelike game. Mecha Force is coming to Meta Quest and Steam VR, and a Kickstarter campaign is available.
